title: Mark Cuban to O'Reilly: I Don't Think Trump Has 'Been Able to Show Any Leadership' in WH
text:
Mark Cuban to O'Reilly: I Don't Think Trump Has 'Been Able to Show Any Leadership' in WH Published February 14, 2017 Facebook 0 Twitter 0 livefyre 0 Email Print 
By Josh Feldman | Mediaite 
Mark Cuban appeared with Bill O’Reilly tonight and told him he’s not very impressed with how President Trump has done in the past few weeks: 
“I don’t think he’s been able to show any leadership. I don’t think he’s taken responsibility for the White House, and I don’t think he’s shown them any direction.”
